---
title: Pub-Style Organic Beef Shepherd’s Pie with White Cheddar & Thyme Mashed Potatoes
description: No matter the weather, is there anything better than homey, comforting classics that warm you from the inside out? If you wholeheartedly agree, look no further! Enter: our chefs’ ode to the classic shepherd’s pie. The base is a rich, tomatoey beef filling chock full of fresh veggies and herbs. On top, swoops of creamy, thyme-flecked mashed potatoes are sprinkled with sharp white cheddar, then broiled to create an irresistibly cheesy crust. It all bakes up in one dish, making it easy as...well, you get it!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/637ba2589b40a13f7a003166-2d9ebd15.jpg
